{"title":"卖儿娘　新区歌之一","authors":["甄崇德"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":9,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"卖儿娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新区歌之一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甄崇德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大同有个侯大庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侯大庄有个卖儿娘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是为娘不疼儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是为娘坏心肠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大同城墙团团转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘的冤曲说不完："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先骂灰鬼阎锡山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽兵抓丁打内战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绳子一条，枪一杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丈夫抓进保卫团，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两眶眼泪流个干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天款，明天捐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼上场不见面；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"租子交不上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主黑心肝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二斗租子红了眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸一张，笔一杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一盘算子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逼个亲娘把儿卖！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲娘怎舍亲生孩？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩儿怎舍亲娘怀？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩的眼泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把娘的心滴穿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩的哭声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把娘的魂哭散。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躺下来，睡不安；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐起来，心里乱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸一把，两手颤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱一抱，是空怀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闭眼，看见孩；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睁眼，孩不见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肚里不知饿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上不觉寒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有意寻短见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心上结记孩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有心上前把孩见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可恨高墙深院"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄狗蹲门前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主那容见？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青天、黄天、老蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀娘的，你是那个天？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声炮响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了救命的共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁墙套城墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大同的敌人投了降！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党领来了好军队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好军队解放了侯大庄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侯大庄建立了好政权，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好政权救出了侯大娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侯大娘换下旧衣穿新衣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸上喜来人精神。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀抱亲生儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑眼里噙着泪花花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一句一句，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着解放回来的亲人儿讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱的苦，咱的冤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去的冤苦对谁谈？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩的爹呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提起心里酸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱土里受苦，土里害；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱土里刨食，土里灾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种的谷，收的棉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃的、穿的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两手空空，不见面！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年没吃过一顿稠米粥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半辈子穿不上一件新衣衫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到后来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地抢去没半垄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"房子顶租没半间；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枝枪杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绑走个你；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一盘算子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逼去咱的孩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常言说：人不该死，有人救，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了救命的活神仙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这笔冤仇才得算！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱没种来，分咱地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱没住来，分咱房；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要亲人，人见面；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我讨孩儿，孩儿重新抱在怀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好光景，还怕过不好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦根子，只怕挖不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦的，酸的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党给咱除了个净；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缺的，少的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党给了咱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你快上前线，杀蒋贼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在家里，忙生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（九月于大同）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}